  "text": "A mm-wave voltage-controlled oscillators is a key component in any radar or communication system. Ultra low power and low phase noise VCOs have been reported previously [CITATION_1] but at the expense of reduced frequency tuning range. A frequency tuning range of more 20% is obtained in [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] at the cost of large die area and power consumption.",
